{"tid":680141,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實，Karius有無諗過佢隊友既感受？","createTime":"2018-05-27T03:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T09:37:11.000Z","uid":149494,"like":271,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"bdab17ec94c609bc7e5d7efc4143cfe3794b2545","tid":680141,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T03:57:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O8zGLyoYkGA?t=478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO8zGLyoYkGA%3Ft%3D478&d=2vFTFNp9xPePz9ek5j223%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f9e1834b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O8zGLyoYkGA?t=478</a><br />\n<br />\n尤其第三球，佢D隊友見到個波入左果下果種崩潰.....<br />\n<br />\n一黎因為呢球波基本上判了利記死刑，二黎D隊友係不敢相信，條友可以一場波內柒一次仲唔夠，仲要柒多次.....<br />\n<br />\n仲話D隊友無風度唔安慰佢...大佬佢有無諗過人地成年既努力比佢派兩次膠抹殺哂...."},{"pid":"9948497b5c8bbb0cee090f2cee8bf503f313fe3f","tid":680141,"uid":149494,"like":203,"dislike":9,"score":194,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:14:12.000Z","msg":"成日話安慰安慰<br />\n<br />\n你唔好彩就話安慰你姐<br />\n<br />\n你自己廢,仲要累到隊友(同事),仲想同事安慰返你,真係痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n連登仔成日將自己代入D弱者心態黎諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1876be914f0c9d3e2f17d7962a4610d7c7d7537","tid":680141,"uid":131369,"like":102,"dislike":1,"score":101,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"其實karius4強對羅馬已經派左幾球膠 但係因為前鋒入波多 所以先好似無咩問題<br />\n 最錯係高普仲出佢 你試下其他龍錯幾次已經唔會再見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3276411ee55e0c9dfab85878739cba98e395a623","tid":680141,"uid":34442,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"除左你話隊友既努力比佢抹殺左 大佬你踢波收咁高人工 都犯錯犯到同朋友打fifa用個龍玩野咁 好似琴晚球彩阿鵬講搵葉鴻輝打仲好啦"},{"pid":"efac058d25da8a760b6ff7d015da3a162804cc29","tid":680141,"uid":30768,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:34:19.000Z","msg":"個球員廢都唔屌得，唔知以為平時自己撐個隊啲人踢得差冇屌過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b27710b1b4e90499e97fecfd89c35de09996fed","